            <p class="description">Face recognition systems will connect the world in a way never experienced before. This project started based on me and my friends' experience from having difficulty distinguishing between foreign characters when we watched movies or drama. People like us can be the user for this project as we begin, but through the research I recognized a large number of people with facial recognition disorders world wide. I believe that if people with facial recognition disorders use this program to identify faces when viewing videos, it will create greater inclusion and synergy.</p>

